<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">小数平方法，两数相乘，如果两个乘数之和为整百、整千......等数时，可将较小乘数乘以整百、整千......后，再减去较小乘数的平方，此差就是要求的积。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">975×25=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 975×25</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=25×1000-25×25</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=25000-625</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=24375</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>